Show real-time statistics for active streams.

Examples: audiomirror-cli stats audiomirror-cli stats --stream-id 1

Usage: audiomirror-cli stats [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --stream-id <STREAM_ID>
          

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
